Reading
Consider the history: That Time When Women Stopped Coding
What occurred during the same time as the beginning of the decline of women in computer science? When personal computers entered the home. 
Why does it matter that males had been playing on computers growing up? They can get used to the tech, explore concepts and have more time working out problems. 

Review the data: Employee breakdown of key technology companies
Ask the question: Why diversity matters to your tech company
When are diversity efforts most successful? When everyone feels included. 
Why do diverse companies perform better? They are more creative and have a different way of approaching the problem. 
Give an example of how a diverse company can serve a diverse user base or vise-versa. Different groups can address issues unique to their group which can create an impact on the company's culture. 
